com.pingidentity.sdk.oobauth

Class OOBAuthStatusChangeReceiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pingidentity.sdk.oobauth.OOBAuthStatusChangeReceiver

  • public class OOBAuthStatusChangeReceiver
extends Object
    A class which accepts status change notifications from OOBAuthPlugin implementations. This may improve the responsiveness of notifications sent to requesting applications/clients.
    Since:
    9.3
    See Also:
